{
  "stem": "3973.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So this is what life was like in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] What unfortunately, as great a movie as it was, concentrated too much on the positive aspect, Schindler and the survivor.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Did not show what I was hoping would be shown about life on the-- amongst less fortunate ones.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It had some of this, but far from enough.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "At any rate, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to cut the story short, my brother arrived.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They closed up the plant later on-- not the plant, the camp in-- in Rakowice.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he immediately wound up in, again, [INAUDIBLE], the master tailor [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So he, again, had his position.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I didn't see much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "He was in a different barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We didn't see each other at all, as far as I know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Then in 1944, they asked for volunteers for assignment in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Nobody volunteered.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "This was a bad thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "But things were so bad, I said, we're going to volunteer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Instead, they took us to Zakopane, which is a resort area in Poland, very beautiful.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "But there were 150 of us assigned to build-- to divert a mountain stream, to build a hydroelectric plant.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I mean, this was murder, unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "This kind of trying to pull stones out of the water and there's still snow and cold.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And-- and terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Anyway, we did three months at Zakopane, from April to July of 1944.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "150.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then we came back to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that time, we were issued stripes for the first time, striped uniforms.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was totally an SS concentration camp, under the jurisdiction of the Gestapo, and all this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because before it was not.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So things got changed for the worse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anyway, I was there for a month.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
